title: High Flying Haaland
description:
The FC crew continue to react to Erling Haaland's wondergoal vs Borussia Dortmund and break into the archives to compare the game winner to goal by the late Johan Cruyff. Plus, the guys reflect on Graham Potter's first match in charge, question if Barcelona can take a moral victory from their loss to Bayern Munich and dismiss Neymar's yellow card for a celebration vs Maccabi Haifa.
